attrs.name: clearable
attrs.defaultValue: The default value of this attribute is false.

attrs.name: placeholder
attrs.desc: Placeholder text in the text box

attrs.name: value-key
attrs.desc: Enter the key name for display in the suggestion object.

attrs.name: value
attrs.desc: This parameter is mandatory. Enter a bound value.

attrs.name: debounce
attrs.desc: Obtain the recommended input dejitter delay.
attrs.defaultValue: The default value of this attribute is 300.

attrs.name: placement
attrs.desc: Menu pop-up position; The optional value of this attribute is top / top-start / top-end / bottom / bottom-start / bottom-end
attrs.defaultValue: The default value of this attribute is bottom-start.

attrs.name: popper-class
attrs.desc: Class name of the Autocomplete drop-down list box

attrs.name: size
attrs.desc: Set the component size. The value can be medium, small, or mini.

attrs.name: trigger-on-focus
attrs.desc: Whether to display the suggestion list when the text box is focused
attrs.defaultValue: The default value of this attribute is true.

attrs.name: select-when-unmatched
attrs.desc: Indicates whether to trigger the select event when pressing Enter when the input does not have any matching suggestions.
attrs.defaultValue: The default value of this attribute is false.

attrs.name: label
attrs.desc: Label text associated with the text box

attrs.name: prefix-icon
attrs.desc: Icon on the header of the text box

attrs.name: suffix-icon
attrs.desc: Icon at the end of the text box

attrs.name: hide-loading
attrs.desc: Whether to hide the loading icon during remote loading
attrs.defaultValue: The default value of this attribute is false.

attrs.name: popper-append-to-body
attrs.desc: Indicates whether to insert the drop-down list into the body element. When a fault occurs in locating the drop-down list, you can set this attribute to false
attrs.defaultValue: The default value of this attribute is true.

attrs.name: fetch-suggestions
attrs.desc: This method is used to return input suggestions. It is returned by calling callback(data:[]) only when your input suggestions are resolved.

attrs.name: highlight-first-item
attrs.desc: Whether to highlight the first item in remote search suggestions by default
attrs.defaultValue: The default value of this attribute is false.

slots.name: prefix
slots.desc: Content in the text box header

slots.name: suffix
slots.desc: Content at the end of the text box

events.name: select
events.desc: This event is triggered when a suggestion item is selected. The callback parameter is: Selected Suggestions
